OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA cloudy day with rain
OL,6,Fspreading eastwards across all parts
OL,7,Fin the morning. Drier and brighter
OL,8,Fweather following on behind during the
OL,9,Fafternoon, reaching all but the far
OL,10,Feast by evening.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FCloud and rain soon clearing
OL,13,Fthe far east. Otherwise dry and clear
OL,14,Ftrough the evening and overnight
OL,15,Fallowing a quite widespread frost to
OL,16,Fdevelop.
OL,17,
OL,18,CFriday:FIt will be a cold start with
OL,19,Fsome frost on Friday, then a dry and
OL,20,Fsunny day.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
